  ('pukao-6f0ba476-moex-00186', 'pukao-6f0ba476', 'pukao-6f0ba476-moex-112-e38ac4c6', 'sub-pukao-6f0ba476-03', NULL, 'essay', '請依我國加值型及非加值型營業稅法規定，回答下列問題：
